CAPE TOWN, South Africa, April 23, 2019/APO Group/ -- 
                                                        
                            The Africa Women Innovation and Entrepreneurship Forum (AWIEF) (AWIEForum.org) is pleased to announce the 3rd edition of the AWIEF Awards.
        
                                    
                    
                        
                                                
                        
                        
